node.text:
Just in case you missed it, here’s a quick recap from the Steve Harvey Invitational Golf Classic presented by @lexususa. Thank you Lexus for being our presenting sponsor and champion for the life work that The @harvey.foundation has committed to. 

With your support we are able to change the lives of disadvantaged youth by cultivating the next generation of responsible leaders and providing educational enrichment, mentoring, life transformation skills, and global service initiatives. 

Thank you to all of our participants and sponsors for your continued support!

___

#Cocacola
#Chickfila 
#Microsoft

node.text: Fathers, sometimes our children just need that one moment of our support to guide them in the right direction or launch their dreams. Here's a story of how my father did that for me.

node.title: My father was my biggest supporter.

node.text:
Not being successful is hard too. Let me tell you the difference between the two. 

Difficulties are a part of your journey to success but there is joy in the journey to success. #motivation #steveharvey

node.text: Behind every moment of adversity there's a lesson and a blessing. You just got to hang in there to see what it is.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Steve Harvey on August 07, 2021 tagging @vaultempowers. May be an image of 1 person, suit and text that says '1 SEPT. 7 7PM EST DON'T SLIP THIS FALL VAULT! LIVE COACHING CALL'.

node.text:
Join me for my live coaching call on Tuesday, September 7 at 7PM EST / 4PM PST for all Vault 365 Members. Gain knowledge on enhancing your productivity, focusing on your happiness, and revisiting the goals on your vision board when you attend this session. Join @vaultempowers today and take advantage of this once in a lifetime opportunity to learn and interact with me! Link in bio to learn more.
https://go.vaultempowers.com/septembercoachingcall/

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Steve Harvey on August 03, 2021 tagging @kirkfranklin, and @vaultempowers. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'KIRK FRANKLIN LIVE COACHING CALL TONIGHT'.

node.text:
TONIGHT at 7PM EST / 4PM PST one of my good friends, @kirkfranklin, will be hosting a Coaching Call on my learning platform @vaultempowers. By attending, you'll gain knowledge in the following areas: 

1. Achieving success 
2. Staying focused on your goals 
3. Achieving the battles within 

Don't miss this once in a lifetime opportunity to get you headed in the right direction to achieving your goals in life. There's still time to register! Link in bio to learn how you can attend this session today.

node.text:
Just in case you missed it, here’s a quick recap from the Steve Harvey Invitational Golf Classic presented by @lexususa. Thank you Lexus for being our presenting sponsor and champion for the life work that The @harvey.foundation has committed to. 

With your support we are able to change the lives of disadvantaged youth by cultivating the next generation of responsible leaders and providing educational enrichment, mentoring, life transformation skills, and global service initiatives. 

Thank you to all of our participants and sponsors for your continued support!

___
